'''Mi’kmaq'''

#An [[aboriginal]] people residing in the Canadian provinces of [[Nova Scotia]], [[Prince Edward Island]], [[New Brunswick]], and [[Quebec]], and in the U.S. cities of [[Boston]] and [[New York City]].
#The [[polysynthetic]] Eastern [[Algonquian]] [[language]] spoken by this people, closely related to [[Maliseet]] and [[Passamaquoddy]].

